snippet.title: Snowboarders : Kiri Adventures trailer ( Winter Edition )
snippet.description:
Snowboarders: Kiri Adventure (Winter Edition)

Play "Snowboarders: Kiri Adventures" a snowboarding game in which you pick as many coins as you can while doing backflips in the snowy hills. Avoid the rocks! Super cool graphics and chill music. 

Controls:-

Press X/Space to jump and hold X/Space to do backflips!
Avoid Rocks!
Features:-

Chill , Calm , Cozy music  take a cup of coffee and start snowboarding !
Beautiful Graphics 
Can do Backflips , grinds and many more...
Relaxing feel takes yours stress off.
Credits :-

Game developer:- Kiri
